section.typography-section.main-section
  h2.section-header#typography Typography

  h3.sub-section-header#headings Headings
  p Headings <code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> through <code>&lt;h5&gt;</code> are available. You can also apply <code>.h1</code> through <code>.h5</code> classes to match header styles without display block.
  .prism-example.headers
    .example-content
      h1 h1: Prism Skylabs Heading
      h2 h2: Prism Skylabs Heading
      h3 h3: Prism Skylabs Heading
      h4 h4: Prism Skylabs Heading
      h5 h5: Prism Skylabs Heading
    .example-code
      pre
        code
          ='<h1>h1: Prism Skylabs Heading</h1>\n'
          ='<h2>h2: Prism Skylabs Heading</h2>\n'
          ='<h3>h3: Prism Skylabs Heading</h3>\n'
          ='<h4>h4: Prism Skylabs Heading</h4>\n'
          ='<h5>h5: Prism Skylabs Heading</h5>'

  h3.sub-section-header#body-text Body text
  p The default <code>font-size</code> for all elements is 14px. There is both a large (16px) and small (12px) size that can be applied to paragraphs or spans. Paragraphs have a <code>margin-bottom</code> of 1em.
  .prism-example.p
    .example-content
      p.large Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Aenean hendrerit sollicitudin mi, a congue sapien lacinia in. Maecenas viverra massa vel aliquam suscipit. Aliquam sodales erat in elit lacinia, eget feugiat enim feugiat.
      p Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Aenean hendrerit sollicitudin mi, a congue sapien lacinia in. Maecenas viverra massa vel aliquam suscipit. Aliquam sodales erat in elit lacinia, eget feugiat enim feugiat.
      p.small Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Aenean hendrerit sollicitudin mi, a congue sapien lacinia in. Maecenas viverra massa vel aliquam suscipit. Aliquam sodales erat in elit lacinia, eget feugiat enim feugiat.
    .example-code
      pre
        code
          ='<p class="large"> ... </p>\n'
          ='<p> ... </p>\n'
          ='<p class="small"> ... </p>'
  .prism-example.span
    .example-content
      span.large Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.
      span Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.
      span.small Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.
    .example-code
      pre
        code
          ='<span class="large"> ... </span>\n'
          ='<span> ... </span>\n'
          ='<span class="small"> ... </span>'

  h3.sub-section-header#alignment-classes Alignment classes
  p Alignment classes are used to easily set the alignment on text elements.
  .prism-example
    .example-content
      p.text-left Left algined text.
      p.text-center Center aligned text.
      p.text-right Right aligned text.
      p.text-justify Justified text.
      p.text-nowrap No wrap text.
    .example-code
      pre
        code
          ='<p class="text-left">Left aligned text.</p>\n'
          ='<p class="text-center">Center aligned text.</p>\n'
          ='<p class="text-right">Right aligned text.</p>\n'
          ='<p class="text-justify">Justified text.</p>\n'
          ='<p class="text-nowrap">No wrap text.</p>'

  h3.sub-section-header#transformation-classes Transformation classes
  p A collection of easy to apply, semantic button styles. Suggested use is outlined in the comments below.
  .prism-example
    .example-content
      p.text-lowercase Lowercased text.
      p.text-uppercase Uppercased text.
      p.text-capitalize capitalized text.
    .example-code
      pre
        code
          ='<p class="text-lowercase">Lowercased text.</p>\n'
          ='<p class="text-uppercase">Uppercased text.</p>\n'
          ='<p class="text-capitalize">capitalized text.</p>'
